'''M'dweshuu''',<ref name="TOR">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref> also called '''M'dweshuu Nova''',<ref name="GG12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref><ref name="TEGtAS">[[The Essential Guide to Alien Species (real-world book)|''The Essential Guide to Alien Species'']]</ref><ref name="EAOC" /> was a [[Nova/Legends|nova]] in [[Hutt Space/Legends|Hutt Space]]. The [[Nikto/Legends|Nikto]] homeworld of [[Kintan/Legends|Kintan]] was in a neighboring system. [[Radiation/Legends|Radiation]] from M'dweshuu caused a high mutation rate in the inhabitants of Kintan. Some Nikto, understanding the effect that M'dweshuu had on their species, formed sects such as the violent [[Cult of M'dweshuu]] to worship the star.

